  body
    .bazaar-wrap
      section.section-hero
        .container
          .stars
          h1 Review &amp; Win!
          h2 Write a product review for a chance to <span>WIN $250</span>
          .text-special Once a Month
          a.choose-product(href="#browse") Choose a Product
      
      section.section-how-to-enter
        h1 How To Enter
        .img-how-to-enter
          .img-callout 
            h3 To Submit a Review
            p Use this link below each product name.
          img(src="img/kwikset/how-to-gfx.jpg", alt="")

        ol.list-how-to-enter
          li.step-1
            h2.txt-find Find your product
            p Use the tool below to find for your favorite Kwikset product. 

          li.step-2
            h2.txt-write Write Your Review
            p Just click "Write a Review" and complete the form to be automatically entered. It's that easy! NO PURCHASE OR PAYMENT OF ANY KIND IS NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN THIS SWEEPSTAKES. A purchase will not increase your chances of winning. <a href="#">Click here</a> to view the complete sweepstakes rules.

      section.section-tips
        .container
          h1 Tips on Writing Reviews
          ul.list-tips
            li 
              h2.tip-be-real Be Real
              p Write about your own experience and explain why you liked or disliked the product. Be as accurate as possible, and include both the positive and negative aspects of your experience.

            li
              h2.tip-be-informative Be Informative 
              p Write about the specifics of the product you are reviewing; design, ease of use, ect. What makes the product unique.

            li.cl-sm
              h2.tip-be-respectful Be respectful
              p Not every experience with a product is going to be perfect. We are happy to receive constructive criticism, it helps us make better products. Please refrain from using profanity, obscene comments or spiteful remarks.

            li
              h2.tip-avoid Avoid
              p Email addresses, URLs, phone numbers, physical addresses or other forms of contact information. Advertisements, “spam” content, or references to other products, offers or web sites

